{"tid":991740,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《大叔的愛》出完電影版 會再拍第二季","createTime":"2019-01-22T15:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T05:32:58.000Z","uid":27064,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"673e1a48a9b1bb54206325c4653d2bd6494b938f","tid":991740,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"日本朝日電視台的BL神劇《大叔的愛》去年4月播映後在日本及亞洲掀起熱潮，男主角田中圭、林遣都及吉田鋼太郎亦人氣急升。朝日電視台於去年底落實開拍電影版，幕前幕後齊集上陣，今年夏天在日本上映。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而昨日更宣布《大叔的愛》第二季將開拍，預定年中至明年3月前播映，至於續集的演員和内容則未有披露</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本電視及電影監製協會主辦的《Elandor賞》公布得獎名單，劇集《大叔的愛》的4位監製三輪祐見子、貴島彩理、神馬由季、松野千鶴子獲監製獎表揚，男主角田中圭則獲新人賞，其餘獲新人賞的藝人還有志尊淳、葵若菜、永野芽郁、中村倫也、松岡茉優。電影《屍殺片場》的導演上田慎一郎和監製巿橋浩治獲監製獎，頒獎禮將於2月7日在東京舉行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190122210112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190122210112&h=5c2106db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190122210112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190122210112&h=ec1c548b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190122210112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122210003188-0122_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190122210112&h=6d3931ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f33b058a33fff5d9dca67ba9ec1a4b54c5164b84","tid":991740,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:15:06.000Z","msg":"小春春<img src=